cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with video surveillance data analysis, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses clustering and classification, which are related to machine learning and data mining, making cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely category. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper discusses query-by-example. The paper also involves structured representation and modeling, which are related to machine learning and statistical methods, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category. Finally, the paper discusses behavior annotation, which involves natural language processing techniques, making cs.CL (Computation and Language) a possible category as well.
